299
00:26:07,678 --> 00:26:09,118
Bergulat?

300
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:12,911
Bergulat, secara harfiah?

301
00:26:12,912 --> 00:26:15,918
Ya, wanita pertama memukulnya
karena jaket bertopinya...

302
00:26:15,919 --> 00:26:18,512
