321
00:27:42,943 --> 00:27:45,784
...rekaman ini terekam dari
langit-langit di Ruang Venesia.

322
00:27:46,792 --> 00:27:50,782
Nah, mulai sekarang...

323
00:27:50,783 --> 00:27:54,199
...fokuskan konsentrasimu pada layar.

324
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:56,387
Tn. Ahn Sung Goon?

325
00:27:57,842 --> 00:28:01,772
Aku dari Kantor Polisi Gangnam.
Bisa minta waktunya sebentar?

326
00:28:02,558 --> 00:28:06,990
- Tentu, apa soal Dokter Kang?
- Benar.

327
00:28:10,393 --> 00:28:14,364
Sekarang...

328
00:28:14,852 --> 00:28:17,098
...kau ada di galeri.

329
00:28:18,087 --> 00:28:22,225
Tak ada seorangpun dan sangat tenang.

330
00:28:22,909 --> 00:28:24,881
Kau aman.

331
00:28:26,530 --> 00:28:31,046
Di ruangan ini,
kau bisa melakukan apapun.

332
00:28:31,466 --> 00:28:33,089
Kau bisa...

333
00:28:33,458 --> 00:28:35,485
...melihat semuanya.

334
00:28:37,652 --> 00:28:39,580
Nah...

335
00:28:39,581 --> 00:28:40,974
...berhenti.

336
00:28:42,055 --> 00:28:44,097
Kau akan fokus.

337
00:28:45,913 --> 00:28:47,631
Perlahan-lahan...

338
00:28:47,632 --> 00:28:49,283
...kau akan ingat.

339
00:29:26,037 --> 00:29:27,273
Kau aman.

340
00:29:27,274 --> 00:29:29,362
Tarik nafas perlahan-lahan.

341
00:29:53,006 --> 00:29:54,647
Jangan khawatir.

342
00:29:55,009 --> 00:29:57,387
Aku yang menciptakan dunia ini...

343
00:29:57,387 --> 00:30:01,061
...dan aku takkan
membawamu ke tempat berbahaya.

344
00:30:01,062 --> 00:30:02,837
Takkan.

345
00:30:05,764 --> 00:30:07,480
Percaya padaku.

346
00:30:07,481 --> 00:30:09,205
Buka hatimu padaku.

347
00:30:10,396 --> 00:30:12,507
Ingatan burukmu...

348
00:30:12,742 --> 00:30:14,876
...akan kuhapus.

349
00:30:27,637 --> 00:30:31,412
Ini bukan karena aku
tak percaya padamu.

350
00:30:33,865 --> 00:30:37,219
Itu karena aku tak
percaya dengan diriku.

351
00:30:38,527 --> 00:30:43,769
Bukankah kebanyakan pasien
menemuimu karena masalah itu?

352
00:30:45,112 --> 00:30:50,408
Karena tak percaya diri sendiri, mereka
menderita sakit hati dan berbagai penyakit.

353
00:30:51,021 --> 00:30:52,617
Benar.

354
00:30:52,618 --> 00:30:54,326
Tepat.

355
00:30:55,524 --> 00:31:00,146
Karenanya... aku butuh
dokter percaya padaku.

356
00:31:10,011 --> 00:31:11,820
Itu...

357
00:31:11,821 --> 00:31:13,787
...siapa?

358
00:31:13,788 --> 00:31:16,431
Ah, dia teknisi CT kami.
Kenapa kau bertanya?

359
00:31:17,684 --> 00:31:21,369
Tak pa-pa, cuma...

360
00:31:24,636 --> 00:31:27,977
Oh, Eun Chang.
Sesiku baru selesai.

361
00:31:28,012 --> 00:31:33,151
Karena perjalanan butuh waktu 3 jam,
kita bisa berangkat sekitar jam 8.

362
00:31:45,754 --> 00:31:49,504
<i>[Sekali lagi kau
nyalakan alarm bodoh itu...]</i>

363
00:31:51,399 --> 00:31:53,010
