00:37:08,134 --> 00:37:10,770
<i>- Robin.
- Robin?</i>

397
00:37:10,771 --> 00:37:12,729
<i>Dia memanggilku Robin?</i>

398
00:37:14,046 --> 00:37:15,771
Ada apa?

399
00:37:16,003 --> 00:37:17,708
